---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | VortKart®"
  description="VortKart® Terms of Service — the terms and conditions governing your use of our website and commercial go kart products and services."
  canonical="https://vortkart.com/terms"
>
<style>
.legal-page{background:var(--dark);padding-top:calc(var(--nav-height) + 60px);padding-bottom:80px}
.legal-container{max-width:860px;margin:0 auto}
.legal-header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px}
.legal-header h1{font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,48px);margin-bottom:12px}
.legal-header .label{color:var(--primary);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;display:block}
.legal-updated{color:var(--gray-3);font-size:14px}
.legal-content{color:var(--gray-2);font-size:16px;line-height:1.8}
.legal-content h2{color:var(--white);font-size:24px;margin:40px 0 16px;font-weight:700}
.legal-content h3{color:var(--white);font-size:18px;margin:28px 0 12px}
.legal-content p{margin-bottom:16px}
.legal-content ul{margin:12px 0 20px 20px}
.legal-content li{margin-bottom:8px}
.legal-content a{color:var(--primary);text-decoration:underline}
.legal-content strong{color:var(--white)}
.legal-card{background:var(--dark-3);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:24px;margin:24px 0}
.legal-card h3{margin-top:0}
.legal-toc{background:var(--dark-2);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:40px}
.legal-toc h3{color:var(--white);font-size:16px;margin-bottom:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em}
.legal-toc ol{margin-left:20px}
.legal-toc li{margin-bottom:6px}
.legal-toc a{color:var(--gray-2);text-decoration:none;transition:var(--transition)}
.legal-toc a:hover{color:var(--primary)}
.legal-back{text-align:center;margin-top:48px}
</style>

<section class="legal-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="legal-container">
      <div class="legal-header">
        <span class="label">Legal</span>
        <h1>Terms of <span class="highlight">Service</span></h1>
        <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: June 24, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <nav class="breadcrumb" style="justify-content:center;margin-bottom:32px">
        <a href={`${base}/`}>Home</a>
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
        <span>Terms of Service</span>
      </nav>

      <div class="legal-toc">
        <h3>Table of Contents</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><a href="#acceptance">Acceptance of Terms</a></li>
          <li><a href="#use-of-site">Use of Our Site</a></li>
          <li><a href="#products">Products &amp; Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="#quotes">Quotes &amp; Pricing</a></li>
          <li><a href="#orders">Orders &amp; Payment</a></li>
          <li><a href="#warranty">Warranty &amp; Returns</a></li>
          <li><a href="#ip">Intellectual Property</a></li>
          <li><a href="#disclaimer">Disclaimer</a></li>
          <li><a href="#liability">Limitation of Liability</a></li>
          <li><a href="#indemnification">Indemnification</a></li>
          <li><a href="#governing-law">Governing Law</a></li>
          <li><a href="#changes">Changes to Terms</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact">Contact Us</a></li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <h2 id="acceptance">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>Welcome to VortKart&reg; International. By accessing and using our website (the "Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms") and all applicable laws and regulations. If you do not agree with any of these Terms, please do not use our Site.</p>
        <p>These Terms apply to all visitors, users, and others who access or use the Site. By submitting a quote request or contacting us through the Site, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms.</p>

        <h2 id="use-of-site">2. Use of Our Site</h2>
        <h3>2.1 Permitted Use</h3>
        <p>You may use our Site for lawful purposes only, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Browsing our products and services</li>
          <li>Requesting quotes and information</li>
          <li>Contacting us for business inquiries</li>
          <li>Accessing publicly available content</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2.2 Prohibited Conduct</h3>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use the Site in any way that violates applicable laws or regulations</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the Site</li>
          <li>Interfere with or disrupt the Site or servers</li>
          <li>Submit false, misleading, or fraudulent information through our forms</li>
          <li>Use automated systems (bots, scrapers) to extract data without permission</li>
          <li>Reproduce, duplicate, or resell our content without authorization</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="products">3. Products &amp; Services</h2>
        <p>VortKart&reg; manufactures and supplies commercial go karts, racing chassis, and provides track design and turnkey karting solutions. All product specifications, images, and descriptions on our Site are provided for general information purposes only.</p>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify, discontinue, or update any product or service at any time without prior notice. Actual products may vary from images shown on the Site.</p>

        <h2 id="quotes">4. Quotes &amp; Pricing</h2>
        <div class="legal-card">
          <ul>
            <li>All quotes provided through our Site are <strong>estimates</strong> and are subject to final confirmation</li>
            <li>Prices are subject to change based on material costs, exchange rates, and order specifications</li>
            <li>Quotes are typically valid for <strong>30 days</strong> from the date of issuance</li>
            <li>Shipping, customs duties, and taxes are not included unless explicitly stated</li>
            <li>A formal purchase order is required to lock in pricing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 id="orders">5. Orders &amp; Payment</h2>
        <h3>5.1 Order Process</h3>
        <p>After receiving and accepting a quote, you must submit a formal purchase order. Order confirmation is subject to product availability, credit verification, and receipt of agreed-upon deposit.</p>

        <h3>5.2 Payment Terms</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>A deposit of <strong>50%</strong> is typically required to initiate production</li>
          <li>Balance is due before shipment unless other terms are agreed in writing</li>
          <li>Accepted payment methods will be specified in the invoice</li>
          <li>Late payments may incur additional fees</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5.3 Delivery</h3>
        <p>Delivery timelines are estimates based on current production schedules. We are not liable for delays caused by force majeure events, customs clearance delays, or shipping carrier delays.</p>

        <h2 id="warranty">6. Warranty &amp; Returns</h2>
        <div class="legal-card">
          <h3>Warranty</h3>
          <p>VortKart&reg; products come with a manufacturer's warranty covering defects in materials and workmanship. Warranty periods vary by product:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Electric karts:</strong> 24 months on frame, 12 months on electrical components</li>
            <li><strong>Gas karts:</strong> 24 months on frame, 12 months on engine</li>
            <li><strong>Racing chassis:</strong> 12 months on welds and frame structure</li>
            <li><strong>Spare parts:</strong> 6 months from purchase date</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Warranty does not cover normal wear and tear, improper maintenance, modification, misuse, or racing damage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="legal-card">
          <h3>Returns</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Custom-manufactured products are <strong>non-returnable</strong></li>
            <li>Standard spare parts may be returned within <strong>14 days</strong> of receipt, subject to a restocking fee</li>
            <li>Returns must be authorized in writing before shipping</li>
            <li>Products must be in original, unused condition</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 id="ip">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content on this Site, including but not limited to text, graphics, logos, images, product designs, and software, is the property of VortKart&reg; International and is protected by copyright, trademark, and other intellectual property laws.</p>
        <p>The VortKart&reg; name and logo are registered trademarks. Unauthorized use of any trademarks or content is strictly prohibited.</p>
        <p>You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, or create derivative works from any content on this Site without our express written permission.</p>

        <h2 id="disclaimer">8. Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>The information on this Site is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. We do not warrant that the Site will be uninterrupted, secure, or error-free, or that any information is complete, accurate, or current.</p>

        <h2 id="liability">9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, VortKart&reg; International shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, special, or exemplary damages arising from use of or inability to use the Site, any information obtained from the Site, or product use outside of intended specifications.</p>
        <p>Our total liability for any claim arising from the use of our Site shall not exceed the amount you paid us for the specific product or service giving rise to the claim.</p>

        <h2 id="indemnification">10. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>You agree to indemnify and hold harmless VortKart&reg; International, its officers, directors, employees, and agents from any claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including attorney's fees) arising from your use of the Site, your violation of these Terms, or any false or misleading information you submit.</p>

        <h2 id="governing-law">11. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which VortKart&reg; International is registered, without regard to conflict of law provisions. Any disputes shall be resolved through good-faith negotiation first, and if unresolved, through arbitration or the appropriate courts.</p>

        <h2 id="changes">12. Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting the revised Terms on this page. Your continued use of the Site after any changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.</p>

        <h2 id="contact">13. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions or concerns about these Terms of Service, please contact us:</p>
        <div class="legal-card">
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:sales@vortkart.com">sales@vortkart.com</a></li>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +1 (234) 567-890</li>
            <li><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Motorsport Drive, Karting District, CA 90001</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="legal-back">
          <a href={`${base}/`} class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
